\begin_inset Formula $M_{\iota}Y$
\end_inset

 on 
\begin_inset Formula $M_{\iota}X_{1}$
\end_inset

, and the OLS estimates is exactly the same as 
\begin_inset Formula $\widehat{\beta}_{1}$
\end_inset

